{"tid":2074322,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"湯家驊：有些人評論國安法時「跳到最極端」、「危言聳聽」","createTime":"2020-06-22T04:33:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T09:08:59.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"86ddbb238335a9b25782f5251222f67482c8e908","tid":2074322,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T04:33:52.000Z","msg":"行政會議成員湯家驊認為，港區國安法草案提到由特首委任處理案件的法官，估計每宗案件程序會涉及九至十名法官，最好的處理方法是由首席大法官負責任命。他相信特首任命前，可能都要參考首席大法官的意見。他批評社會有認識司法系統的人，在評論港區國安法時會跳到最極端、最不利一國兩制的結論，認為批評不能危言聳聽，或作出無事實根據的推測。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊又表示，社會有很強的聲音認為部分法官不能處理涉及國安法案件，由特首指派是一種妥協；又認為內地刑法較從前已有很大改善，對人權有保障。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1316611&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1316611%26csid%3D261_341&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F6EbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=663b2af7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1316611&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"d1531f56b859f0207029a08f5863187b75326f94","tid":2074322,"uid":205162,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T04:36:17.000Z","msg":"11哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc5521fa7dc496e925ffcdd16c4ba4e839f60af7","tid":2074322,"uid":53026,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T04:38:44.000Z","msg":"最極端係你，一食就要食最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"388b8bd9906284f7f0ffc31cc96e15f642133610","tid":2074322,"uid":125017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T04:40:41.000Z","msg":"封左頂咪無最極端囉"},{"pid":"39d954032dc78cd5c0c05b3b1ac2dfe068559b88","tid":2074322,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T04:42:22.000Z","msg":"瀾翻去支那嫖宿幼女啦，成日衝出黎柒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n正視聽：若抗爭方向不隨局勢改變，只會無謂地損兵折將<br />\n香港街頭抗爭目標，亦都係街頭抗爭最大效果；&ldquo;攬炒&rdquo;已經達到，今次搞蟈安法其實仲攬炒過上年出老解。<br />\n宜家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">跟著落黎就係引渡全球政府同議會（尤其美國）對付支那以及滅共</span></strong>，所以大家重點應該著眼帶出清晰民意授權比各國政府做野，畫面靚+全球廣泛報導（類似反蟈安法銅鑼灣自由行）係最理想，用選票帶出民意亦十分重要。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要小心五毛、熱狗放負風向：美國唔會幫我地（舊年年尾）-》英國係廢國無用架（今年年頭）-》歐盟奶共唔會幫我地（宜家）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家要記住，香港生路只有一條：救香港人+攬炒促進支爆+重建香港。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有支爆，香港獨立或者歸英等重建方案全部都係痴人說夢。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n未來幾個月至支共瓦解期間大家要做嘅事：1.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">走資</span></strong>2.全球救生艇<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">救手足加有細路既黃絲家庭</span></strong>（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）3.比足夠<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民意授權，敦促美國以至各國凌遲式消除香港作為支那獲得外資渠道</span></strong>，包括但不限於：禁止美國個人或公司投資港股，暫停接受香港用美元結算等等4.最後就真係等<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>支那自己爆</strong></span>"},{"pid":"df6acbf439e8b00cbfcb094ceeb8d89f97430e35","tid":2074322,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc5521fa7dc496e925ffcdd16c4ba4e839f60af7","tid":2074322,"uid":53026,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T04:38:44.000Z","msg":"最極端係你，一食就要食最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T04:44:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"332db09dca0a48015a8996cb423b7a86bd2caed8","tid":2074322,"uid":132587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T04:48:04.000Z","msg":"你食幼幼年齡都去到最極端啦"},{"pid":"7492ba6e5262c7d7a12239e438cb7b537c0d51b0","tid":2074322,"uid":121197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T04:51:00.000Z","msg":"幫緊你戴頭盔咋喎<br />\n到時真係咁做咪I told you so囉<br />\n立於不敗之地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ba0e169b58768c625415d69431f94718f5c1f1","tid":2074322,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T04:51:01.000Z","msg":"知唔知點解跳到咁極端？ 就係因為你段野寫到唔清唔楚 想人自我審查 彩你都有尾 <br />\n咩叫你知咩做得咩唔做得？ <br />\n我唔知wo 寫清楚少少 我唔係共產黨肚入邊條蟲"},{"pid":"0fd6bfe21f500635a7e4e7fbb4fa938cb1fd3c01","tid":2074322,"uid":60057,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T04:51:14.000Z","msg":"偏偏共產黨就係鍾意係灰色地帶中走到最極端"},{"pid":"d54956f75c82e5dfa422dfd2ae206b36c5e00340","tid":2074322,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T04:54:09.000Z","msg":"掃晒人地d雜誌夠極端啦"},{"pid":"907584888a51827b37939243a57a20fc93659d79","tid":2074322,"uid":335434,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d1531f56b859f0207029a08f5863187b75326f94","tid":2074322,"uid":205162,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T04:36:17.000Z","msg":"11哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T04:56:34.000Z","msg":"有些人評論非法性交罪時「跳到最極端」、「危言聳聽」。即使罪成輕則只會判感化令，特定案情下才會判監2年，希望曾犯此罪者當機立段即時自首。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2019/12/1576651981_Fa-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2019%2F12%2F1576651981_Fa-1280w.jpg&h=07865be7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20160628/s00001/1467110734394SL4_95BD2A378417F77A7935781682BDFF3F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20160628%2Fs00001%2F1467110734394SL4_95BD2A378417F77A7935781682BDFF3F.jpg&h=96e31027&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d29d147edcfff6f087e16e3345038ed544f1747","tid":2074322,"uid":171788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T04:56:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bnpyY1N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnai